Therefore I choose Monsters of Rock Platinum Edition because its remastered AOR/classic‑rock compilation format, curated sequencing, sing‑along anthems, and collectible presentation best satisfy my stated tastes for polished, melodic, guitar‑forward classic rock. I reject the Bond compilation not for lack of quality, but because its cinematic/pop orientation doesn't match my specific preference for lush, harmony‑rich, studio‑polished AOR/classic‑rock CDs.

