- I also appreciate analog‑feeling remasters only when they preserve dynamics and snap rather than dull clarity; layered electric‑guitar attack, tasteful (sparingly used) organ, lush multi‑tracked harmonies, big sing‑along choruses, and careful song‑forward sequencing.
